      • scene

        private ArScene scene
        A collection of graphical objects to be displayed in the 3D view of MainActivity. They are stored here to avoid recreation when the user moves to another activity (for example the MapsActivity) and back. However, as the GLSurfaceView is reinitialized on restarting the Activity all Gl context in the scene (shaders, VBOs, textures) should be recreated.
